************How Webpage works *********************

- internet global network of computers and devices
- each has IP address assigned by internet provider 73.158.6.61
- private local IP address router has a public IP
- computers talk with eachother using the TCP/IP protocol
- HTTP handles web traffic (requests/responses)
	application layer protocol
	browser and server
	one of more FTP, SMTP,

Websides files stored on computers that run a piece of software called a web server (Apache, Nginx)

Hosting companies provide space on a server for your websa you can have yur own computer but it is expensive get a server, shared hosting

domain name - can be purchased fro registrars and linked to your hosting account

DNS is used to map IP addresses to domain names

type address in web brownes DNS server maps isthe name with address and does the HTTP request to the server Server will send the response

