************** font size *******************************

defoult is 16px
space in between the line (in em)
line-height: 1.6em;


Absolute units:
cm Centimeters
mm Milimeters
in Inches
px Pixels(1px = 1/96th of 1in)
pt Points (1pt = 1/72 of 1in)
pc Picas pias(1pc = 12pt)

Relative Units:
% To parent element
em To font size of paret element multiplayer
rem To font size of root element (html by default 16px)
vw To 1% of viewport width
vh To 1% of viewport height

font-weight
font-style

