all 255 white
all 0 black
hexadecimal
numbers 0-9 or and letters A-F
all 0 black
all f whites
six simbols

ff - red ff - green ff - blue 
all the same we can cut by half 
ex black #000000 = #000
ex dark grey #333333 = #333


